1
00:00:15,839 --> 00:00:17,270
(The state of Nanzhao laid low.)

2
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:20,500
(They sent out a team of envoys
to hold a peaceful negotiation with Great Tang.)

3
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:23,639
(But our people
were tormented by poisonous parasites.)

4
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:25,490
(They couldn't afford
to delay the situation any longer.)

5
00:00:26,679 --> 00:00:28,750
(They were willing to trust me)

6
00:00:29,060 --> 00:00:31,180
(and tried abdominal incision
to remove the parasites)

7
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,949
(just to survive.)

8
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:36,110
(I finally understood why)

9
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:38,400
(what it meant to be
the princess consort of Great Tang)

10
00:00:38,439 --> 00:00:39,990
(and the imperial coroner.)

11
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:43,470
(The most precious thing about me
was never my identity.)

12
00:00:43,759 --> 00:00:46,750
(It was the hope and belief
that I could bring to the people.)

13
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:50,549
(In the past, I only used my scalpel
to perform autopsies.)

14
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:52,309
(But today,)

15
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,589
(I'm using it to save people.)

16
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:11,070
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

17
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:15,830
♪Build a bridge between life and death♪

18
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:20,110
♪Hear a voiceless declaration♪

19
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:25,310
♪Break disguises, cross illusions♪

20
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:28,079
♪A fleeting life and delusions♪

21
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:30,919
♪The surface always conceals♪

22
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:36,110
♪Separate cause and effect♪

23
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:38,839
♪A twisted path, rising and falling♪

24
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:41,479
♪Seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

25
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:46,319
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

26
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:51,350
♪No matter how far, I gaze at the light♪

27
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:56,910
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

28
00:01:57,200 --> 00:02:02,390
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

29
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:07,670
♪The deeper truth is buried, it grows♪

30
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:10,030
♪Until it is set free♪

31
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:24,479
=Imperial Coroner S2=
(Adapted from Idle Girl's The Constable's Wife)

32
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:27,559
(This story is entirely fictional.)

33
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,830
=Episode 27=

34
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,430
Second Prince.

35
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,309
Watch out, Longsheng!

36
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,349
Longsheng?

37
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,069
Longsheng!

38
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:01,830
No one is to enter

39
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:02,710
without my orders!

40
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,950
General Xiao.

41
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,390
Longsheng!

42
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:13,789
Stop him.

43
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,230
Longsheng!

44
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,029
I see now.

45
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,309
So, your so-called peaceful negotiation

46
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:23,950
is just a feast of betrayal, huh?

47
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,749
Move out of the way.

48
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,510
I need to return
and report this to Father.

49
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,670
You murdered him, didn't you?

50
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,510
Second Prince, you may not leave

51
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,510
until the investigation is over.

52
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,830
You guys already murdered my brother.

53
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,519
And now,
you wish to pin the blame on me?

54
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,990
After all that time spent negotiating,

55
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:44,550
you're the person who wants the peaceful
negotiation to be canceled the most.

56
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,990
You're just afraid that he might
achieve success in the peaceful negotiation,

57
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,980
helping him to ascend
the throne after his return.

58
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:51,150
After that, he might
silence you for good.

59
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,150
Commandery Prince An,

60
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,589
is it not enough to kill him alone?

61
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,349
Do you wish to murder me as well?

62
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:59,589
Would you rather

63
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,760
initiate war and
cause the people to suffer

64
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,029
just for your selfish desires?

65
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,990
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

66
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,029
But this is what I understand.

67
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,960
If you guys don't allow me to leave,

68
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,550
I'll end myself here and now.

69
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,110
Think about it.

70
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,909
What'll happen if two princes of Nanzhao

71
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,989
die here at the same time?

72
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,070
What will my Father think about it?

73
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,469
And, how can you guys face him?

74
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,989
Think about it!

75
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,469
Let him leave.

76
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,549
You Longsheng was assassinated.

77
00:05:05,550 --> 00:05:07,790
The culprit was wearing the armor
of Great Tang's guards.

78
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,549
They intend to pin the blame
on Great Tang.

79
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,390
Relay my orders.

80
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,429
Prepare for war.

81
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,669
What?

82
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:19,589
Second Prince has already returned.

83
00:05:19,590 --> 00:05:21,590
And, he has brought
Eldest Prince's body with him.

84
00:05:21,639 --> 00:05:22,789
Someone!

85
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,429
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

86
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:25,909
Go!

87
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,270
Relay my order.

88
00:05:30,759 --> 00:05:31,549
Muster our troops.

89
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:34,349
I'm going to join the battle myself!

90
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,490
- Yes, Your Majesty!
- Yes, Your Majesty!

91
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:45,510
You kept performing
the incision one after another.

92
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,549
You didn't sleep a wink for 24 hours.

93
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,150
You should take a break.

94
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:03,029
It feels sore.

95
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,190
This is the Neiguan acupoint.

96
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,909
If it feels sore when I apply pressure,

97
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,830
that means
you've overexhausted yourself.

98
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,750
What about this?

99
00:06:14,050 --> 00:06:15,750
I'll head back
and make you something nice.

100
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,710
Wait for me.

101
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:52,950
Your Highness.

102
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,190
What's wrong with Chu Chu?

103
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,349
She's overexhausted.

104
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,830
I'm going to prepare food for her.

105
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,750
What happened?

106
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,318
You Longsheng is dead.

107
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:23,229
You Longsheng is dead?

108
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:29,270
You're awake.

109
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,190
Your Highness.

110
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:34,429
You Chen'an desired
to kill his brother from the start.

111
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,390
Although it was a dangerous plan,
the timing was meticulous.

112
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:40,390
Now, we can ruin the peaceful negotiation
by just shouldering the blame.

113
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,679
But the king of Nanzhao
doted on him the most.

114
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,070
He would surely avenge him.

115
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,589
Do we still have to go to war?

116
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:55,710
Is there really no turning back?

117
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:57,270
Going to war

118
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:59,150
is merely the worst-case scenario.

119
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:01,870
We must be fully prepared
for all scenarios.

120
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,989
You just need to tend
to the patients in the temple

121
00:08:05,090 --> 00:08:06,429
and remove the parasites in them,

122
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:09,310
dispelling the allegations
in the process.

123
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,989
That'll be more than enough.

124
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,830
You Chen'an acted hastily.

125
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,670
It's inevitable
that he'll leave behind some traces.

126
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,390
I've already given
Zhou Han all the leads.

127
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,400
I hope things can still turn around.

128
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,830
Let me in!

129
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,669
Chu Chu!

130
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,589
Chu Chu!

131
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,229
Father?

132
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,270
Chu Chu,

133
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:34,069
are you doing okay?

134
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,189
Father,

135
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,709
I...

136
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,150
It's okay.

137
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,870
(Chu Ping, Chu Chu's father)
I know everything.

138
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,990
After we received a letter from you,

139
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,909
your grandfather fell sick.

140
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,990
Grandfather fell sick?

141
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:52,150
Now, he has already gotten much better.

142
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,390
But he was worried about you

143
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,189
after hearing
that you were risking your life

144
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:56,789
to save the people here.

145
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:58,880
He was worried
that something might happen to you.

146
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,150
That's why he urged me to visit you.

147
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,750
Silly girl,

148
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,150
it must've been tough on you.

149
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,150
Father, I'm sorry.

150
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,429
It's all my fault.

151
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:15,230
I failed to look after Chu Chu.

152
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,150
Your Highness,

153
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:19,270
please don't say that.

154
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,949
Although we're poor,

155
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,549
we do have discerning eyes.

156
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,750
Nanzhao is at fault here.

157
00:09:26,090 --> 00:09:28,029
Chu He sacrificed himself
for the greater good.

158
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,709
He's the pride and joy of our family.

159
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,390
But Your Highness,

160
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,239
Chu Chu

161
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,909
is our only child now.

162
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:44,309
Please ensure

163
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:47,470
her safety, okay?

164
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,549
Father...

165
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:50,949
Don't worry.

166
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:53,990
I'll definitely do my best
to look after Chu Chu.

167
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:57,150
Once everything settles down,

168
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,390
I'll take you and
Grandfather to Chang'an

169
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:01,390
and let you two enjoy
your retirement years here.

170
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,350
Good.

171
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,429
That sounds great.

172
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:09,669
Excellent.

173
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:27,549
You were fine
when you left on your journey.

174
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,510
But now,

175
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,390
you're already gone!

176
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,429
I need to write to Father.

177
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:36,949
We will attack Jiaozhou.

178
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,549
I will seek revenge

179
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:40,590
for my late husband!

180
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:42,750
Eldest Princess Consort.

181
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,709
Actually,

182
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,990
there's a hidden reason

183
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,669
behind Eldest Prince's death!

184
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:56,669
All of you, leave.

185
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,230
Tell me everything

186
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,669
you know.

187
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:17,669
The culprit behind
Eldest Prince's murder

188
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,510
is actually

189
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:21,110
Second Prince.

190
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,990
You Chen'an?

191
00:11:23,519 --> 00:11:24,990
Since when was he bold enough

192
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,120
to murder his brother
during the peaceful negotiation?

193
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,870
At the time of the incident,

194
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:31,789
only Xiao Jinyu,

195
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:34,549
Jing Yi, and the two princes
were in the tent.

196
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:36,590
According to Second Prince,

197
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:39,870
the soldiers of Great Tang were
bound by their old grudges,

198
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:42,829
thus assassinating Eldest Prince
of their own accord.

199
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:45,230
But something felt off.

200
00:11:45,679 --> 00:11:47,990
Of all the times to assassinate him,

201
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:51,038
why must they assassinate him
right before the peaceful negotiation

202
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,270
was resolved?

203
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,750
This surely has nothing
to do with grudges.

204
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:01,870
I'm sure Second Prince was afraid that
Eldest Prince might return triumphantly

205
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,050
after resolving
the peaceful negotiation successfully.

206
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,390
Do you have evidence?

207
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,390
After my suspicion was aroused,

208
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:20,189
I stole the murder weapon
during the chaos.

209
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,669
Your Highness, please take a close look.

210
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:25,398
This dagger is the same
as the daggers used by

211
00:12:25,399 --> 00:12:26,750
the soldiers of Great Tang.

212
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,270
But to enhance its durability,

213
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,669
the blade was reinforced by

214
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:31,270
steel.

215
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,150
Steel is in short supply.

216
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:35,949
How could an ordinary soldier
get his hands on it that easily?

217
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:37,709
Thus,

218
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:40,590
I traced the flow
of steel materials in Nanzhao.

219
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:42,429
I launched a secret investigation.

220
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:44,510
Guess what happened?

221
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,949
Just tell me already!

222
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,990
I spotted the design of this dagger

223
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:55,750
in a weapons shop!

224
00:12:55,879 --> 00:12:57,669
And, the owner of the weapons shop,

225
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:58,669
he...

226
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,119
he...

227
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:01,870
He was the subordinate of You Chen'an!

228
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,110
You Chen'an!

229
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:08,470
Your Highness,
please accept my condolences!

230
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:20,970
This dagger is crafted from materials
different from ordinary daggers.

231
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,669
Follow the leads and investigate.

232
00:13:22,810 --> 00:13:24,270
If you find any conclusive evidence,

233
00:13:24,290 --> 00:13:25,900
try to persuade Eldest Princess Consort.

234
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,870
Yes, sir.

235
00:13:52,919 --> 00:13:56,038
Father, although my husband died
for the sake of Nanzhao,

236
00:13:56,039 --> 00:13:57,520
his death is shrouded in injustice!

237
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:59,638
Father, please uphold justice
for my husband

238
00:13:59,639 --> 00:14:00,949
and punish the real culprit!

239
00:14:03,639 --> 00:14:06,110
Father, please uphold
justice for my husband!

240
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:20,669
You animal. You killed your brother
for the sake of glory.

241
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,949
How dare you still pretend?

242
00:14:22,950 --> 00:14:23,798
I'm going to kill you!

243
00:14:23,799 --> 00:14:24,390
Your Highness!

244
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,790
Sister-in-law,
I know you're in a lot of pain

245
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:31,949
because of Longsheng's death.

246
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:33,750
I understand your feelings.

247
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:35,990
It's just that as his brother,

248
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:37,350
I cannot bear the blame

249
00:14:37,799 --> 00:14:39,870
for my brother's death.

250
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:42,038
I was there to witness it all
when a soldier of Great Tang

251
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:43,309
assassinated my brother.

252
00:14:43,919 --> 00:14:45,150
Sister-in-law, I wonder

253
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:47,669
who instigated you to say that.

254
00:14:47,799 --> 00:14:49,750
What goes around comes around.

255
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,110
Do you think you can
hide the truth from everyone?

256
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:54,350
Father,

257
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,549
I have evidence.

258
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:58,470
The dagger used by the culprit

259
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:01,150
was forged in a weapons shop
owned by You Chen'an's subordinate.

260
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,669
The truth will be revealed
once we interrogate him.

261
00:15:07,279 --> 00:15:07,909
Father,

262
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,350
I'm innocent.

263
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,780
As for the evidence
Sister-in-law has pointed out,

264
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:13,150
I know nothing about it.

265
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,870
Even if the weapons shop
were under my name,

266
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,918
there are plenty of customers every day.

267
00:15:17,919 --> 00:15:19,709
How could I know each of their details?

268
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,669
Sister-in-law, how could you be sure

269
00:15:24,519 --> 00:15:26,750
that someone wasn't trying
to frame me here?

270
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:27,829
Who else do you think

271
00:15:28,279 --> 00:15:30,270
hates my husband as much as you?

272
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,949
Father,

273
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:37,470
my brother already died in Chang'an
because of Peacock.

274
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:40,390
And, my husband was murdered
in cold blood as well!

275
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,150
Father!

276
00:15:43,279 --> 00:15:44,719
Please uphold justice for my husband!

277
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,119
Please uphold justice for me!

278
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:46,949
Father,

279
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:49,150
I cannot bear to hear

280
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:50,870
Sister-in-law's heartbreaking remark.

281
00:15:51,519 --> 00:15:53,189
That's enough!

282
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:56,110
Great Tang hasn't invaded us,

283
00:15:56,159 --> 00:15:58,309
yet we're already
falling out with each other.

284
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,750
Aren't you guys embarrassed?

285
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:04,189
Eldest Princess Consort,

286
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,309
I will

287
00:16:11,759 --> 00:16:13,549
investigate this case prudently.

288
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,789
However,

289
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:17,558
you need to stop messing around

290
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:18,870
before the truth is revealed.

291
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,390
Perhaps this is a scheme

292
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:24,390
devised by Great Tang
to drive a wedge between you two!

293
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,909
Both of you, get up.

294
00:16:40,039 --> 00:16:42,750
Return and keep vigil for Sheng.

295
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,669
All of you may leave.

296
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:06,110
You're no longer young.

297
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:07,870
It's time for you to establish a family.

298
00:17:08,079 --> 00:17:09,350
It's time

299
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,870
to expand the royal lineage.

300
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,350
Father,

301
00:17:12,759 --> 00:17:14,350
compared to establishing a family,

302
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:15,870
I would rather

303
00:17:16,079 --> 00:17:17,390
become a great hero,

304
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,870
just like you.

305
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,990
I want to make a name for myself
before doing anything else.

306
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,509
Here.

307
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,949
My dear son.

308
00:17:29,519 --> 00:17:30,830
This is great.

309
00:17:31,279 --> 00:17:32,590
This is great!

310
00:17:34,500 --> 00:17:36,950
How dare you pave a path for yourself
with your brother's life

311
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:39,790
in the name of success?

312
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:43,390
Father, what are you saying?

313
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:44,879
I don't understand at all.

314
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:46,639
You don't understand?

315
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:48,310
I understand it all too well!

316
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,358
I didn't expose you

317
00:17:54,359 --> 00:17:57,830
in front of
Eldest Princess Consort this afternoon

318
00:17:57,880 --> 00:18:00,870
because you couldn't bear
the crime of killing your own brother!

319
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,590
What an excellent scheme you'd devised.

320
00:18:04,799 --> 00:18:07,278
You knew that you would
be the only son left.

321
00:18:07,279 --> 00:18:08,700
You knew that I wouldn't touch you

322
00:18:08,710 --> 00:18:11,469
even though you were at odds
with your brothers!

323
00:18:13,279 --> 00:18:14,110
Father,

324
00:18:15,359 --> 00:18:16,550
although Longsheng and I

325
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:17,949
were at odds,

326
00:18:18,799 --> 00:18:20,469
they were merely brotherly quarrels.

327
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:23,350
Why would I commit such a grave blunder?

328
00:18:24,279 --> 00:18:25,229
Father,

329
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,590
the only thing I wish to do

330
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,189
and are able to do

331
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,150
is to contribute to Nanzhao

332
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,949
in my own small way.

333
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:38,669
I know Sister-in-law
had misunderstandings about me

334
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,749
because of Longsheng.

335
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,830
But I've never blamed her for it.

336
00:18:45,519 --> 00:18:46,909
Father, I only hope

337
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:50,190
that you won't fall for
Great Tang's divide-and-conquer scheme.

338
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:00,030
What are you doing?

339
00:19:00,759 --> 00:19:02,110
Father,

340
00:19:03,119 --> 00:19:04,669
now, you're the only person

341
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,509
I care about in this world.

342
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,150
If you don't trust me,

343
00:19:09,759 --> 00:19:11,150
I shall return

344
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,150
my life to you!

345
00:19:42,079 --> 00:19:43,358
The King has never been late

346
00:19:43,359 --> 00:19:44,709
to a single court session.

347
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,199
What's going on today?

348
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,909
Don't tell me something happened to him.

349
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,300
Do not spout such nonsense.

350
00:19:53,079 --> 00:19:53,949
Everyone,

351
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,790
The King suffered a stroke last night.

352
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:58,509
According to the law,
Second Prince will be the acting ruler.

353
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,870
The King was still fine yesterday.

354
00:20:11,319 --> 00:20:12,749
How did he...

355
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:13,830
Everyone,

356
00:20:14,759 --> 00:20:15,590
Father

357
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:17,790
was already depressed
due to Longsheng's death.

358
00:20:18,450 --> 00:20:20,310
He suffered a sudden stroke
when he summoned me

359
00:20:21,050 --> 00:20:22,399
to join him for dinner last night.

360
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:25,509
If so, has the King issued a decree
declaring you as the acting ruler?

361
00:20:28,810 --> 00:20:31,429
As it was a sudden stroke,
the King lost his ability to write.

362
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,959
But in the midst of his condition,

363
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,780
he clung desperately
to Second Prince's hand,

364
00:20:34,799 --> 00:20:36,310
signaling him to take over the throne.

365
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:39,700
I have no intention of being the ruler.

366
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,909
But now, Longsheng is gone.

367
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:46,269
And, Father is seriously ill.

368
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:49,350
I can't bear to see Nanzhao
fall into chaos.

369
00:20:50,390 --> 00:20:51,278
Since that's the case,

370
00:20:51,279 --> 00:20:53,078
Second Prince, please accept the mission
in this time of crisis

371
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:54,269
and be the acting ruler.

372
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,310
The King has always been
in the pink of health.

373
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,989
Now, he's suddenly sick?

374
00:20:58,559 --> 00:21:00,509
Who knows if this is a scheme?

375
00:21:01,079 --> 00:21:02,669
Great General, are you saying

376
00:21:03,559 --> 00:21:04,870
that you wish to be the ruler?

377
00:21:05,079 --> 00:21:06,709
Stop framing me!

378
00:21:07,519 --> 00:21:08,669
Reporting in!

379
00:21:11,300 --> 00:21:13,199
The Great Tang army
is stationed at the border,

380
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:15,070
only ten li away from our forces!

381
00:21:15,559 --> 00:21:16,719
They're too much!

382
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:17,550
Do another scout!

383
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,390
Yes, sir!

384
00:21:20,079 --> 00:21:21,269
Nanzhao and Great Tang

385
00:21:21,279 --> 00:21:23,229
are at loggerheads now.

386
00:21:23,559 --> 00:21:24,590
If anything goes wrong,

387
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,239
our state will be crushed.

388
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,558
Nanzhao cannot exist without a ruler.

389
00:21:27,559 --> 00:21:29,500
Second Prince, please assume
the throne immediately,

390
00:21:29,519 --> 00:21:31,020
stabilize the morale
of the people and the army,

391
00:21:31,039 --> 00:21:32,038
and resolve the crisis.

392
00:21:32,039 --> 00:21:33,269
That's right.

393
00:21:33,519 --> 00:21:36,709
- Please consider the greater good!
- Please consider the greater good!

394
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:38,150
Consider the greater good, huh?

395
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:40,870
Fine.

396
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:43,870
I'm willing to be the acting ruler.

397
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:44,870
Of course,

398
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,230
I'll return the throne to Father

399
00:21:46,519 --> 00:21:47,669
as soon as he has recovered.

400
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:50,518
Second Prince, you have no intention
of usurping the throne.

401
00:21:50,519 --> 00:21:52,340
And, you're devoting yourself
to the state and its people.

402
00:21:52,359 --> 00:21:53,870
If anyone tries to doubt you again,

403
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,509
they'll be the traitors of our state!

404
00:22:03,559 --> 00:22:05,550
Second Prince is righteous!

405
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:08,350
- Second Prince is righteous!
- Second Prince is righteous!

406
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,269
After what Sister-in-law had done,

407
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:31,150
Father would surely doubt me.

408
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,550
Now that I've come this far,

409
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:35,870
I can't afford to let
anything go wrong again.

410
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,749
Those who try to oppose me

411
00:22:38,079 --> 00:22:39,310
shall die.

412
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,070
Father,

413
00:22:56,519 --> 00:22:57,469
please be appeased.

414
00:23:13,119 --> 00:23:14,189
All of you may leave.

415
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,189
Close the door.

416
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,030
Second Prince,

417
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:26,310
all is done.

418
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:30,669
You know what to do
with those two, right?

419
00:23:31,359 --> 00:23:32,550
Do a clean job.

420
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,709
I don't want to hear any rumors.

421
00:23:36,799 --> 00:23:37,590
Second Prince,

422
00:23:38,759 --> 00:23:39,590
but...

423
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:41,310
Why are you panicking?

424
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:44,110
Right now,

425
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:46,669
you're the person I trust the most.

426
00:23:47,559 --> 00:23:49,790
All that awaits you is wealth and glory.

427
00:23:51,119 --> 00:23:51,830
Okay?

428
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,598
(He murdered his mother,)

429
00:23:53,599 --> 00:23:54,598
(his brother,)

430
00:23:54,599 --> 00:23:55,669
(and now, his father.)

431
00:23:56,519 --> 00:23:58,909
(I've known too many secrets of his.)

432
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,150
(I'm afraid I'll be silenced)

433
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:02,879
(before I get to enjoy
all the wealth and glory.)

434
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:04,639
- I need to see the King!
- I need to see the King!

435
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:05,429
Let us in!

436
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,550
Your Highness.

437
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:09,550
How's Father?

438
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,078
The King never woke up.

439
00:24:11,079 --> 00:24:12,150
The royal physician
already examined him.

440
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,580
He said it was the doing
of accumulated fatigue,

441
00:24:13,599 --> 00:24:15,430
accompanied by sudden surges and dips
in one's emotional state.

442
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,870
He needs to rest and recuperate.

443
00:24:18,839 --> 00:24:19,838
Bring me the medicine.

444
00:24:19,839 --> 00:24:20,558
I'll feed him personally.

445
00:24:20,559 --> 00:24:21,310
Yes, Your Highness.

446
00:24:22,520 --> 00:24:23,429
Bring us the medicine.

447
00:24:26,839 --> 00:24:27,790
Father, here.

448
00:24:36,839 --> 00:24:37,669
Father.

449
00:24:57,440 --> 00:24:58,269
Let's wait.

450
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:03,749
Nanzhao has suffered heavy losses
in military strength.

451
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:06,269
If we do go to war with Great Tang,

452
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,150
I'm afraid

453
00:25:08,599 --> 00:25:09,949
a difficult war awaits us.

454
00:25:12,039 --> 00:25:13,390
Therefore, no matter what,

455
00:25:13,770 --> 00:25:15,509
we should try
to negotiate peace with them.

456
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:17,909
What about our revenge
for Eldest Prince?

457
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:19,150
Are we going to let them off?

458
00:25:19,799 --> 00:25:21,550
Or are the rumors true?

459
00:25:21,839 --> 00:25:23,269
Is there a hidden reason

460
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,989
behind Eldest Prince's death?

461
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:26,749
Precisely.

462
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:32,518
Great General, since you were one
of Father's most important subjects,

463
00:25:32,519 --> 00:25:33,669
I won't hold it against you.

464
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,719
But in the future, I don't want

465
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,790
to hear such rumors again.

466
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,269
Do you understand?

467
00:25:42,559 --> 00:25:44,150
It is Father's wish to negotiate peace.

468
00:25:44,519 --> 00:25:45,949
To him,

469
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,669
Longsheng's life,

470
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,110
even his own life,

471
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,790
isn't as important as Nanzhao itself.

472
00:25:52,519 --> 00:25:53,429
But of course,

473
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:56,189
we can't just back down all the time

474
00:25:57,119 --> 00:25:58,749
and let them belittle us.

475
00:25:59,119 --> 00:26:00,350
Tell Xiao Jinyu

476
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:02,350
that he needs to come personally

477
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,510
if he wishes
to reinitiate the peaceful negotiation.

478
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,269
All of you may leave.

479
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:09,110
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highness.

480
00:26:12,079 --> 00:26:12,639
Your Highness,

481
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,350
we've successfully performed
the incision for everyone.

482
00:26:14,359 --> 00:26:17,229
But now, the sutured wound
on them is quite large.

483
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,719
It'll definitely cause ulcers.

484
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:21,118
In addition, they already
have a weak constitution.

485
00:26:21,119 --> 00:26:23,150
If we don't treat them promptly,

486
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:24,669
their lives might be in danger.

487
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:29,429
What other herbs do you need?

488
00:26:29,559 --> 00:26:30,399
Honeysuckle flower,

489
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,469
wild chrysanthemum,

490
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:32,749
purple violet herb,

491
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:33,989
and Chinese fan palm seeds.

492
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,038
They can detoxify the blood.

493
00:26:35,039 --> 00:26:36,790
Lady Jing is already on her way
to procure them.

494
00:26:45,799 --> 00:26:46,669
Chu Chu.

495
00:26:48,700 --> 00:26:51,110
I've already checked with
all the apothecaries in the city.

496
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:54,469
There was no problem in procuring them,
except for honeysuckle flowers.

497
00:26:55,359 --> 00:26:56,189
Why don't we

498
00:26:56,799 --> 00:26:58,350
ask His Highness for his opinions?

499
00:26:58,559 --> 00:26:59,150
Don't.

500
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,989
They're already busy enough

501
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,550
dealing with Nanzhao.

502
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:05,189
Let's think of something else ourselves.

503
00:27:05,319 --> 00:27:05,989
Okay.

504
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,070
Chu Chu.

505
00:27:09,319 --> 00:27:10,949
You guys needed herbs, right?

506
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:14,159
Father, why are you bustling about
the moment you arrive?

507
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,719
Didn't I tell you to rest?

508
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:16,399
I'm fine.

509
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,679
I'm still going strong.

510
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,150
I need to stretch my legs anyway.

511
00:27:19,730 --> 00:27:22,669
If you guys need herbs, you can head to
the mountain produce marketplace.

512
00:27:22,670 --> 00:27:24,919
They sell plenty of mountain herbs
and produce there at a low price.

513
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,429
Mountain produce marketplace?

514
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:28,199
Why didn't you tell me about it before?

515
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:30,100
In previous years,
they were able to sell their goods.

516
00:27:30,119 --> 00:27:30,758
But due to the turmoil,

517
00:27:30,759 --> 00:27:31,900
there were fewer and fewer
goods collector.

518
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:33,430
They only come once or twice per month.

519
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:35,199
Gradually, they all started coming
on the 18th day of the month.

520
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,429
Thus, it became a marketplace.

521
00:27:37,839 --> 00:27:39,439
Since you all are so busy,

522
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:40,669
I'll go and procure the herbs.

523
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:42,078
But Father...

524
00:27:42,079 --> 00:27:42,600
I'll be fine.

525
00:27:42,610 --> 00:27:43,358
Staying idle is tormenting.

526
00:27:43,359 --> 00:27:44,078
Zhang Yun,

527
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:45,509
join my father.

528
00:27:45,519 --> 00:27:46,310
Okay, Your Highness.

529
00:27:46,599 --> 00:27:47,390
Don't worry.

530
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:52,669
Find a discreet place

531
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,870
and move him there.

532
00:27:55,530 --> 00:27:57,390
I don't want anyone
to get in contact with him

533
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:59,909
before I ascend the throne successfully.

534
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,550
Yes, Your Highness.

535
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:04,550
Father,

536
00:28:05,599 --> 00:28:07,229
don't blame me for this.

537
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,830
It's about time I took back

538
00:28:10,010 --> 00:28:11,830
the things you stole from
my mother and me.

539
00:28:32,010 --> 00:28:33,830
Honeysuckle flower
is the last herb we need.

540
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,590
We got it!

541
00:28:38,799 --> 00:28:39,749
Physician,

542
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,469
see if this is the herb you want.

543
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,509
This is it.

544
00:28:51,599 --> 00:28:53,269
Is that all?

545
00:28:53,319 --> 00:28:54,669
I'm afraid it's not enough.

546
00:28:59,039 --> 00:29:01,999
The herb seller said there are still plenty
on the innermost rock face

547
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:04,150
if we go up the mountain to the west
from the southern slope.

548
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:05,159
I know where it is.

549
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,558
It's near the temple.
I'll go and harvest them.

550
00:29:06,559 --> 00:29:07,358
Master Chu, please wait.

551
00:29:07,359 --> 00:29:08,680
The herbalist said
that to gather honeysuckle,

552
00:29:08,690 --> 00:29:09,999
one must first traverse a forest.

553
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,838
But the forest is full of
venomous insects and muddy swamps,

554
00:29:11,839 --> 00:29:12,910
and it's easy to get lost.

555
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,550
One might die easily
if they're careless.

556
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:15,870
It's that dangerous?

557
00:29:16,039 --> 00:29:16,989
Father,

558
00:29:17,039 --> 00:29:18,278
how could you hide that from me?

559
00:29:18,279 --> 00:29:19,110
What about this?

560
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,199
I'll take some men and join Master Chu.

561
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,350
We'll make haste.

562
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:23,719
You guys must be careful, then.

563
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,709
I'll go summon my men.

564
00:29:25,359 --> 00:29:26,310
Let's go.

565
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:28,909
Be careful.

566
00:29:29,090 --> 00:29:29,989
Don't worry about it.

567
00:29:43,599 --> 00:29:44,669
Honeysuckle flowers?

568
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:46,709
We found them!

569
00:29:47,759 --> 00:29:48,669
Hurry!

570
00:29:50,770 --> 00:29:52,450
There are indeed
honeysuckle flowers here.

571
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:53,669
Wait.

572
00:29:53,670 --> 00:29:54,798
When picking honeysuckle flowers,

573
00:29:54,799 --> 00:29:56,199
it's best to choose those
that have just begun to bloom.

574
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:58,310
But the ones that aren't in full bloom
have the best medicinal effects.

575
00:29:58,320 --> 00:30:00,150
Try to avoid picking those
with insect bites.

576
00:30:01,350 --> 00:30:03,879
And, please refrain from crushing
the flowers when picking them.

577
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:04,820
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

578
00:30:04,830 --> 00:30:05,679
Remember what he said.

579
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,679
Go and find them nearby.

580
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:07,709
Don't get lost.

581
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:08,860
- Yes, ma'am.
- Yes, ma'am.

582
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:09,709
Please wait!

583
00:30:10,039 --> 00:30:10,550
Here.

584
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,830
Take the whistle.

585
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,949
Master Chu, where did you get it from?

586
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:15,590
I bought it before
entering the mountains.

587
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:16,518
The mountain road is very winding.

588
00:30:16,519 --> 00:30:18,199
If we get lost
or when we're done harvesting,

589
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:19,669
we can blow it to locate the others.

590
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:22,429
I bought too few of them.

591
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:24,790
You two can form a duo and share one.

592
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,669
Let's go.

593
00:30:30,279 --> 00:30:31,390
Safety first, okay?

594
00:30:42,079 --> 00:30:42,870
Where's Master Chu?

595
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,870
I didn't see him.

596
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:44,439
What about you?

597
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,400
I didn't see him either.

598
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:48,318
Split up and look for him!

599
00:30:48,319 --> 00:30:49,390
- Yes, ma'am.
- Yes, ma'am.

600
00:30:50,279 --> 00:30:51,350
Father's missing?

601
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:52,350
Where did he go missing?

602
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:53,590
Your Highness, please don't panic.

603
00:30:53,599 --> 00:30:54,990
Lady Jing and her men
are already looking for him.

604
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:56,038
I'll go and summon more men.

605
00:30:56,039 --> 00:30:57,120
We'll look for him together.

606
00:31:00,319 --> 00:31:01,229
Master Chu!

607
00:31:01,250 --> 00:31:02,078
Have you found him?

608
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:02,870
Not yet.

609
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:04,380
- Continue the search.
- Yes, ma'am.

610
00:31:06,390 --> 00:31:07,469
- Master Chu!
- Leng Yue.

611
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:08,990
- Have you found my father?
- Master Chu!

612
00:31:11,559 --> 00:31:12,590
Let's search over there.

613
00:31:19,839 --> 00:31:20,870
Who are you all?

614
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:22,078
Second Prince...

615
00:31:22,079 --> 00:31:22,709
No, I mean,

616
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,070
the current regent of Nanzhao

617
00:31:24,079 --> 00:31:26,189
wishes to invite you to our palace.

618
00:31:26,279 --> 00:31:27,159
Your father

619
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,229
is waiting for you there.

620
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:29,709
You guys captured my father, huh?

621
00:31:29,839 --> 00:31:31,110
The new king honors the past.

622
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,870
He regrets the death
of his sworn brother.

623
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,749
Therefore, he wants
to console your father.

624
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:36,949
Your Highness, as long as
you're willing to follow us,

625
00:31:37,079 --> 00:31:38,598
your father will be safe.

626
00:31:38,599 --> 00:31:39,269
Just you wish!

627
00:31:39,839 --> 00:31:40,590
Chu Chu,

628
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,830
don't listen to them.

629
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:43,469
My brother is already gone.

630
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,999
I can't afford to lose my father now.

631
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:45,989
But Chu Chu...

632
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:49,990
Since You Chen'an is inviting me there,
that means he has a request to ask of me.

633
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,500
He doesn't dare to do anything to me.

634
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:53,870
Hurry and notify His Highness.

635
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:55,749
Don't worry about me.

636
00:31:56,210 --> 00:31:56,838
But Chu Chu...

637
00:31:56,839 --> 00:31:57,509
Lead the way.

638
00:32:15,279 --> 00:32:16,030
Jinli.

639
00:32:16,599 --> 00:32:18,030
The envoys of Nanzhao are inside.

640
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,830
At this crucial moment,

641
00:32:20,039 --> 00:32:22,909
why would the royal family of Nanzhao
send an envoy to our borders?

642
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,990
And, they insist on meeting you
before telling us about their goal.

643
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,709
After You Longsheng's death,

644
00:32:28,010 --> 00:32:30,790
the King of Nanzhao said that he wanted
to join the battle personally.

645
00:32:31,079 --> 00:32:32,909
But now, there's no news of him.

646
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,110
If it's not a scheme,

647
00:32:35,279 --> 00:32:37,030
I'm sure something has happened to him.

648
00:32:37,250 --> 00:32:39,038
And, there's no news
from Zhou Han as well.

649
00:32:39,039 --> 00:32:40,429
I wonder what's going on.

650
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:41,989
We'll know what they're up to

651
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,590
once we see the envoy.

652
00:32:51,119 --> 00:32:52,030
Commandery Prince An.

653
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,598
Under His Highness's order, we came here

654
00:32:59,599 --> 00:33:02,660
in willingness to reinitiate the peaceful
negotiation between the two states.

655
00:33:03,119 --> 00:33:04,540
Eldest Prince has lost his life,

656
00:33:04,550 --> 00:33:06,630
causing a misunderstanding
between the two states,

657
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:08,229
and ceasing the peaceful negotiation.

658
00:33:08,799 --> 00:33:10,078
Just like Nanzhao,

659
00:33:10,079 --> 00:33:11,669
Great Tang is heartbroken as well.

660
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:14,838
If the King of Nanzhao
is willing to investigate the case,

661
00:33:14,839 --> 00:33:17,669
clear our names,
and reinitiate the peaceful negotiation,

662
00:33:17,759 --> 00:33:19,469
it'll be beneficial to both states.

663
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:21,879
I came here under Second Prince's order.

664
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:24,310
Commandery Prince An,
please head to Nanzhao as an envoy.

665
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:26,909
You must be kidding me.

666
00:33:26,910 --> 00:33:28,850
We're fine
with the peaceful negotiation and all,

667
00:33:28,870 --> 00:33:30,749
but why should we change
the venue to Nanzhao?

668
00:33:32,690 --> 00:33:35,070
The cause of Eldest Prince's death
hasn't been verified yet.

669
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:36,518
For both parties' peace of mind,

670
00:33:36,519 --> 00:33:37,870
it's best not to change locations.

671
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,870
Moreover,

672
00:33:39,039 --> 00:33:40,509
does the King of Nanzhao know about

673
00:33:40,759 --> 00:33:42,189
Second Prince's order?

674
00:33:43,039 --> 00:33:45,310
Commandery Prince An, don't be so hasty.

675
00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:47,070
You should consider it first.

676
00:33:47,279 --> 00:33:49,199
As for Second Prince's order...

677
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:50,070
Your Highness!

678
00:33:52,519 --> 00:33:53,469
This is bad.

679
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,989
We're in trouble.

680
00:34:02,839 --> 00:34:05,310
Chu Chu and Father-in-law
were captured by Nanzhao?

681
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,269
That's right.

682
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:08,290
The person who came said
that it was You Chen'an.

683
00:34:08,519 --> 00:34:10,238
Now, he's already the regent.

684
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,279
He issued the order.

685
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,269
The regent?

686
00:34:12,890 --> 00:34:14,680
A regent will only assume
the king's duties

687
00:34:15,039 --> 00:34:16,309
if the king is unwell.

688
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,789
No wonder the King of Nanzhao
didn't act at all.

689
00:34:19,290 --> 00:34:20,550
Your Highness, you were right.

690
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:22,638
A major upheaval
has erupted within their court.

691
00:34:22,639 --> 00:34:25,309
No wonder that envoy
from Nanzhao was so brazen.

692
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:26,810
He was sure

693
00:34:26,820 --> 00:34:29,790
that I would submit to their request
since they captured Chu Chu and Father.

694
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,110
But you mustn't head to Nanzhao.

695
00:34:31,119 --> 00:34:32,518
It's utter chaos over there.

696
00:34:32,519 --> 00:34:34,229
A den of danger awaits you there.

697
00:34:34,239 --> 00:34:35,879
By then, both you and Chu Chu
will be at their mercy.

698
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:37,390
We would be completely at their mercy.

699
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,150
I have to go.

700
00:34:44,719 --> 00:34:45,389
Jinyu,

701
00:34:45,599 --> 00:34:46,590
calm down and think.

702
00:34:47,599 --> 00:34:48,309
Jinli,

703
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:49,709
I'm very calm.

704
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:51,319
I'm not just heading there
for personal affairs.

705
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:53,319
You Chen'an was never favored
by the King of Nanzhao.

706
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:55,190
His foundation
in the royal court isn't stable.

707
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:57,070
He became the regent out of the blue.

708
00:34:57,180 --> 00:34:58,869
I'm sure his foundation
isn't stabilized.

709
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:01,279
I'm sure he's doing all he can
to lure me to Nanzhao

710
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,430
to ask me for a favor.

711
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,718
If so, Chu Chu and Father-in-law

712
00:35:03,719 --> 00:35:05,269
are safe for now.

713
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:09,829
Your Highness, you're trying to say
that no risk equals no reward, right?

714
00:35:10,679 --> 00:35:12,319
We can only take advantage of the flow

715
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,510
if we know what they desire.

716
00:35:13,519 --> 00:35:15,550
If we can muddy the waters
of Nanzhao even further,

717
00:35:16,119 --> 00:35:17,638
we can secure greater benefits

718
00:35:17,639 --> 00:35:19,550
for Great Tang
in subsequent negotiations.

719
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,829
Taking innocent people hostage
to blackmail them,

720
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:53,709
that's utterly despicable.

721
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:56,189
Aren't you afraid
that people might mock you?

722
00:35:57,190 --> 00:35:58,999
Your Highness,
I once invited you to Nanzhao

723
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:01,110
when we were at the mountain god temple.

724
00:36:01,519 --> 00:36:02,910
I'm just fulfilling my promise here.

725
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,669
I wonder why

726
00:36:05,519 --> 00:36:06,759
you're blaming me for this.

727
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:07,669
You Chen'an,

728
00:36:08,199 --> 00:36:10,349
it seems you're as despicable as always.

729
00:36:10,910 --> 00:36:12,770
I suppose you didn't
receive your regent title

730
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:14,879
through official means, huh?

731
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:15,550
Such audacity!

732
00:36:15,660 --> 00:36:17,500
How dare you show the regent
such disrespect?

733
00:36:17,519 --> 00:36:18,389
Yuluo.

734
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:23,070
There's no need for formalities
between her and me.

735
00:36:24,679 --> 00:36:26,869
Father had a sudden stroke
and fell unconscious.

736
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,349
In all fairness,

737
00:36:28,519 --> 00:36:30,189
I should be the acting ruler.

738
00:36:30,519 --> 00:36:32,078
If so, how do you explain

739
00:36:32,079 --> 00:36:33,470
why you kidnapped Father and me?

740
00:36:34,159 --> 00:36:35,269
I invited you guys here

741
00:36:35,639 --> 00:36:38,430
because I don't want the two states
to go to war again.

742
00:36:38,850 --> 00:36:40,750
I wish to reinitiate the peaceful negotiation
between the two states.

743
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:42,709
However, the royal court
is in chaos right now.

744
00:36:43,039 --> 00:36:44,030
I had no choice

745
00:36:44,159 --> 00:36:45,389
but to do this.

746
00:36:45,600 --> 00:36:48,279
Commandery Princess Consort An,
just treat yourself as a guest here.

747
00:36:48,280 --> 00:36:49,749
Save your breath. Where's my father?

748
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:50,869
Master Chu is safe.

749
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:56,269
Yuluo, take Commandery Princess Consort An
to see Master Chu later.

750
00:36:56,599 --> 00:36:57,990
Treat them well.

751
00:36:58,719 --> 00:36:59,669
Yes, Your Highness.

752
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:14,950
I told you already. I'm not eating.

753
00:37:15,119 --> 00:37:17,590
It's either you let me go,
or I starve myself to death.

754
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,189
Father?

755
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,038
Chu?

756
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:22,829
Father!

757
00:37:24,599 --> 00:37:25,150
Father,

758
00:37:25,239 --> 00:37:26,158
are you hurt?

759
00:37:26,159 --> 00:37:26,869
Let me see.

760
00:37:27,519 --> 00:37:28,829
No. I'm fine.

761
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:30,749
Did they feed you any parasites or poison?

762
00:37:30,780 --> 00:37:31,470
No, they didn't.

763
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:33,189
What are you doing here?

764
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:34,950
Did they blackmail you
by taking me hostage?

765
00:37:36,039 --> 00:37:37,189
I'm so useless.

766
00:37:37,559 --> 00:37:38,359
Before I knew it,

767
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:40,070
they knocked me out and brought me here.

768
00:37:40,079 --> 00:37:41,389
I wanted to help you out.

769
00:37:41,410 --> 00:37:43,110
But now, I've become
your burden instead.

770
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:44,229
Father,

771
00:37:44,599 --> 00:37:45,990
what are you saying?

772
00:37:46,599 --> 00:37:47,799
You only came to help me out

773
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,170
because you were worried about me.

774
00:37:49,199 --> 00:37:51,470
You Chen'an is full of
schemes and trickery.

775
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:53,269
I was the one who dragged you down.

776
00:37:53,599 --> 00:37:55,430
We're a family. Don't say that.

777
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:58,990
Father,

778
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:00,229
don't worry.

779
00:38:00,599 --> 00:38:02,269
His Highness will
do something about this.

780
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,389
I'll try my best to deal with
You Chen'an as well.

781
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,829
Let's act accordingly.

782
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:10,890
(Prefect's Residence)

783
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,669
Jing Yi,

784
00:38:13,159 --> 00:38:16,078
verify with Han Ji the list of personnel
dispatched to Nan Zhao,

785
00:38:16,079 --> 00:38:18,250
the required documents,
and the ceremonial procession.

786
00:38:18,519 --> 00:38:19,110
Understood.

787
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:22,999
Leng Yue, prepare some gifts to present to
the court officials and their wives.

788
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:23,590
Understood.

789
00:38:25,519 --> 00:38:26,349
Chen Feng, Zhang Yun.

790
00:38:26,350 --> 00:38:26,919
Yes, Your Highness.

791
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:29,580
Find some capable but unfamiliar-looking
individuals from Jiaozhou

792
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:31,100
to pose as attendants and accompany us.

793
00:38:31,119 --> 00:38:31,749
- Yes.
- Yes.

794
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:32,999
Go and find Chief Luo.

795
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:34,190
She has plenty of connections.

796
00:38:34,310 --> 00:38:35,389
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

797
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,390
As for the border defense

798
00:38:40,679 --> 00:38:41,869
of Jiaozhou City,

799
00:38:42,159 --> 00:38:43,280
Jinli, I'll leave it to you.

800
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,510
If anything goes wrong,

801
00:38:44,639 --> 00:38:47,229
please disregard us
and mobilize the troops immediately.

802
00:38:49,079 --> 00:38:51,430
Please relay the info to me immediately
if anything happens.

803
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:52,669
You Chen'an

804
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,759
is devious and scheming.

805
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:55,110
You have to be wary of him.

806
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,229
And,

807
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,269
come back in one piece.

808
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,789
Don't worry.

809
00:39:03,159 --> 00:39:04,110
Summon

810
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:07,829
the envoys of Great Tang to the court!

811
00:39:18,599 --> 00:39:20,309
Envoy, why are you not kneeling

812
00:39:20,519 --> 00:39:22,030
in front of the regent?

813
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:24,279
On my way here, I heard from your envoy

814
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:25,960
that the King of Nanzhao
is seriously ill.

815
00:39:26,030 --> 00:39:27,799
Second Prince is
merely acting as the regent

816
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,070
at this time of crisis.

817
00:39:29,290 --> 00:39:31,310
However, there should
only be one ruler in a state.

818
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,110
In all fairness,

819
00:39:33,199 --> 00:39:35,189
we should pay our respect
to the King of Nanzhao.

820
00:39:36,079 --> 00:39:37,749
Otherwise, it would be discourteous.

821
00:39:38,199 --> 00:39:39,869
Commandery Prince An,
you do have a point.

822
00:39:42,199 --> 00:39:43,030
Someone.

823
00:39:43,599 --> 00:39:44,389
Bring Father

824
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:45,669
to the court.

825
00:39:55,199 --> 00:39:56,470
He's something else.

826
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:58,829
He's holding their king hostage
to blackmail the officials,

827
00:39:58,830 --> 00:40:00,880
and he's holding Chu Chu hostage
to blackmail you.

828
00:40:16,310 --> 00:40:18,670
- Greetings, King of Nanzhao.
- Greetings, King of Nanzhao.

829
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:24,430
The envoys of Great Tang
have traveled long and far.

830
00:40:24,530 --> 00:40:25,869
We can tell that you're sincere.

831
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:29,999
Nanzhao will try to reinitiate the peaceful
negotiation as soon as possible.

832
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:31,789
But we haven't avenged
Eldest Prince yet.

833
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,869
That's why His Majesty
fell ill from worry.

834
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:35,990
There's no peaceful negotiation

835
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:37,520
unless they're willing
to give us an account!

836
00:40:37,719 --> 00:40:39,789
Second Prince,
you may be able to withstand it,

837
00:40:40,079 --> 00:40:41,590
but my soldiers and I

838
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:43,229
cannot withstand it!

839
00:41:02,380 --> 00:41:05,420
♪Time drips away
like fading crimson scent♪

840
00:41:05,420 --> 00:41:08,940
♪The hardships of arrival pass
in a fleeting blink♪

841
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:12,060
♪Palm lines carry
the footprints of memory♪

842
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:16,020
♪Leading us out of every winding turn♪

843
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:20,660
♪If two hearts can fly as one
then storms are part of the way♪

844
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:23,940
♪Looking back the sky
has already cleared♪

845
00:41:24,060 --> 00:41:26,580
♪Your branches entwined with mine♪

846
00:41:26,580 --> 00:41:29,980
♪Bound together in mutual reliance♪

847
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:35,180
♪Rugged roads become
the paths of sun and moon♪

848
00:41:35,180 --> 00:41:38,260
♪Fireflies like stars circle
through the seasons♪

849
00:41:39,100 --> 00:41:41,220
♪Shining with the hope of dreams♪

850
00:41:41,220 --> 00:41:45,900
♪This world is no longer in rags♪

851
00:41:46,620 --> 00:41:50,260
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

852
00:41:50,260 --> 00:41:53,540
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

853
00:41:53,940 --> 00:41:56,260
♪Together we face the tides of fate♪

854
00:41:56,260 --> 00:42:00,420
♪Turning the course of heaven and earth♪

855
00:42:00,540 --> 00:42:03,140
♪This love was never easy♪

856
00:42:03,140 --> 00:42:07,540
♪So life and death will not part us♪

857
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:10,460
♪Like sinking into the deep sea♪

858
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:15,460
♪The first breath upon awakening♪

859
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:17,700
♪This bond will never waver♪

860
00:42:17,700 --> 00:42:22,580
♪So we stay together
till our hair turns white♪

861
00:42:22,580 --> 00:42:25,060
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen♪

862
00:42:25,060 --> 00:42:30,100
♪And write the ending of eternity♪

863
00:42:30,140 --> 00:42:32,420
♪This love was never easy♪

864
00:42:32,420 --> 00:42:36,580
♪So I believe without doubt♪

865
00:42:37,220 --> 00:42:39,820
♪Like a thousand sails passing by♪

866
00:42:39,820 --> 00:42:44,740
♪Reaching shore
at the first light of dawn♪

867
00:42:45,220 --> 00:42:47,100
♪This bond will never waver♪

868
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:52,100
♪So joy and sorrow
are no longer ours to choose♪

869
00:42:52,100 --> 00:42:54,500
♪I will prove it
with the rest of my life♪

870
00:42:54,500 --> 00:43:00,260
♪Together at the edge
of the world without an end♪
